{
  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div data-lake-element=\"root\" class=\"lake-engine lake-typography-traditional\" data-parser-by=\"lake2html\"><a name=\"挂载一个主机目录作为数据卷\"></a><h2 id=\"e5be1316\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">挂载一个主机目录作为数据卷</h2><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\">使用 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">--mount</code> 标记可以指定挂载一个本地主机的目录到容器中去。</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><div data-card-type=\"block\" data-lake-card=\"codeblock\" data-card-value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%223c3f1948%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22bash%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%24%20docker%20run%20-d%20-P%20%5C%5C%5Cn%20%20%20%20--name%20web%20%5C%5C%5Cn%20%20%20%20%23%20-v%20%2Fsrc%2Fwebapp%3A%2Fopt%2Fwebapp%20%5C%5C%5Cn%20%20%20%20--mount%20type%3Dbind%2Csource%3D%2Fsrc%2Fwebapp%2Ctarget%3D%2Fopt%2Fwebapp%20%5C%5C%5Cn%20%20%20%20training%2Fwebapp%20%5C%5C%5Cn%20%20%20%20python%20app.py%22%7D\" id=\"3c3f1948\"><div class=\"lake-codeblock-content\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(232, 232, 232); max-width: 750px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><div class=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 16px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><pre class=\"cm-s-default\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">$ docker run -d -P \\\n</span></span><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">    --name web \\\n</span></span><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">    # -v /src/webapp:/opt/webapp \\\n</span></span><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">    --mount type=bind,source=/src/webapp,target=/opt/webapp \\\n</span></span><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">    training/webapp \\\n</span></span><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">    python app.py</span></span></pre></div></div></div><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\">上面的命令加载主机的 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">/src/webapp</code> 目录到容器的 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">/opt/webapp</code>目录。这个功能在进行测试的时候十分方便，比如用户可以放置一些程序到本地目录中，来查看容器是否正常工作。本地目录的路径必须是绝对路径，以前使用 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">-v</code> 参数时如果本地目录不存在 Docker 会自动为你创建一个文件夹，现在使用 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">--mount</code> 参数时如果本地目录不存在，Docker 会报错。</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\">Docker 挂载主机目录的默认权限是 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">读写</code>，用户也可以通过增加 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">readonly</code> 指定为 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">只读</code>。</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><div data-card-type=\"block\" data-lake-card=\"codeblock\" data-card-value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22ca4c029a%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22bash%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%24%20docker%20run%20-d%20-P%20%5C%5C%5Cn%20%20%20%20--name%20web%20%5C%5C%5Cn%20%20%20%20%23%20-v%20%2Fsrc%2Fwebapp%3A%2Fopt%2Fwebapp%3Aro%20%5C%5C%5Cn%20%20%20%20--mount%20type%3Dbind%2Csource%3D%2Fsrc%2Fwebapp%2Ctarget%3D%2Fopt%2Fwebapp%2Creadonly%20%5C%5C%5Cn%20%20%20%20training%2Fwebapp%20%5C%5C%5Cn%20%20%20%20python%20app.py%22%7D\" id=\"ca4c029a\"><div class=\"lake-codeblock-content\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(232, 232, 232); max-width: 750px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><div class=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 16px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><pre class=\"cm-s-default\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">$ docker run -d -P \\\n</span></span><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">    --name web \\\n</span></span><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">    # -v /src/webapp:/opt/webapp:ro \\\n</span></span><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">    --mount type=bind,source=/src/webapp,target=/opt/webapp,readonly \\\n</span></span><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">    training/webapp \\\n</span></span><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">    python app.py</span></span></pre></div></div></div><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\">加了 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">readonly</code> 之后，就挂载为 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">只读</code> 了。如果你在容器内 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">/opt/webapp</code> 目录新建文件，会显示如下错误</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><div data-card-type=\"block\" data-lake-card=\"codeblock\" data-card-value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22cce32c9e%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22bash%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%2Fopt%2Fwebapp%20%23%20touch%20new.txt%5Cntouch%3A%20new.txt%3A%20Read-only%20file%20system%22%7D\" id=\"cce32c9e\"><div class=\"lake-codeblock-content\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(232, 232, 232); max-width: 750px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><div class=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 16px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><pre class=\"cm-s-default\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-